Parliament, Tuesday, 17 September 2019 – The Portfolio Committee on Public Enterprises will tomorrow be briefed by Alexkor on progress made in addressing governance challenges and financial performance.
	
	Furthermore, the committee will be briefed by South African Airways (SAA) on progress made in addressing governance challenges and advancing its developmental objectives.
	
	Details of the meeting:
	Date : Wednesday, 18 September 2019
	Time : 09:30
	Venue : Committee Room V475, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building
	
	ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES
	
	For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
